程序及运行结果： 2 最大值与第一个数交换 输入示例：75 7 2 8 9 3 1 输出示例：After swapped: 9 7 2 8 5 3 1 程序代码： #include &lt;stdio.h&gt;#include &lt;corecrt_malloc.h&gt;int main(void)&#123; int i, n, max = 0, index = 0; printf(&quot;Input n:&quot;); scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;n); int* a = (int*)malloc(n * sizeof(int)); printf(&quot;Input %d integers:&quot;, n); for (i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) &#123; scanf(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;a[i]); if (a[i] &gt; max) &#123; max = a[i]; index = i; &#125; &#125; int b = a[0]; a[0] = a[index]; a[index] = b; for (i = 0; i &lt; n; i++) printf(&quot;%d &quot;, a[i]); return 0;&#125;
